    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1285">
<l>eḻutuṅkāṟ kōlkāṇāk kaṇṇēpōṟ koṇkaṉ </l>
<l>paḻikāṇēṉ kaṇṭa viṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the eyes which see not the pencil that paints it, I cannot see my husband's fault (just) when I meet him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
